# SOLUTION

# The solution is to print the minimum value of the first segment and the maximum value of the second segment.
# The answer is guaranteed to exist because the segments are not empty.

q = int(input())
for i in range(q):
    l1, r1, l2, r2 = map(int, input().split())
    print(l1, r2)
